    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        Switch the account off, and then switch it on to try to reconnect to the
        service.
      </p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <section id="prob-conn-neterror-proxy">
    <title>Proxy euskarria</title>
    <p>Une honetan,<app>Empathy</app> ezin da konfiguratu proxy-rekin lan egiteko.</p>
